                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-5-off17 t18020918-5-crimeloc20"></join>: On the 4th of September, about nine o'clock in the evening, while a man of a mean appearance was trying on a pair of shoes, my wife missed my watch, which had been hanging up where I was at work; it has my name at length in it, it was made for me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18020918-5-person98">
                  ANN 
                  HOWARD
